name: Maze (The Amazing Labyrinth) Free
description:
Maze (The Amazing Labyrinth) is interesting puzzle game for everyone. Get ready to face different types of challenges in the game.

Features
-Amazing Maze Puzzle game everyone.
-HD Quality of Graphics used in the Game.
-50 Different Levels in the game. 10 Levels available in Free Version. Upgrade to Unlock all the Levels.
-Player Interest Increases after every level.
-Fully Tested on iPhone 5,5s,6,6s, 6 Plus & iPad (All).
-Ratings & Feedback Appreciated.
